  "texts": [
    "c GLT DPFU uncertainties are based on the scatter of three measurements, inclusive of flux density model errors, but may be larger due to significant antenna astigmatism.",
    "There is also a ∼15% T * sys uncertainty contributing to the total SEFD uncertainty.",
    "d For the JCMT DPFU, the nighttime value is shown.",
    "e The SMA DPFU uncertainty is based on the dominant 5-15% uncertainty on the phasing efficiency.",
    "The Event Horizon Telescope Collaboration: A&A, 681, A79 (2024)"
  ]
